{"title":"CentOS上通过fdisk分区并挂载硬盘","date":"2022-07-29T09:05:58.159Z","slug":"mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk","comments":true,"tags":["CentOS","CentOS挂载硬盘","fdisk","分区","腾讯云挂载硬盘","腾讯轻量云挂载"],"updated":"2026-05-25T07:58:47.050Z","content":"<h4 id=\"0x00：查看新增的数据盘\">0x00：查看新增的数据盘<a href=\"post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk#0x00：查看新增的数据盘\"></a></h4>  <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fdisk -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>  <div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/fdisk-l.png\" alt=\"查看新增的数据盘\"><br>  <code>/dev/vdb</code>为新增的数据盘</div></p>\n<h5 id=\"0x01：分区\">0x01：分区<a href=\"post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk#0x01：分区\"></a></h5>  <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fdisk /dev/vdb</span><br><span class=\"line\">n</span><br><span class=\"line\">p</span><br><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2048</span><br><span class=\"line\">41943039</span><br><span class=\"line\">p</span><br><span class=\"line\">w</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>  也可以依次输入<code>n</code>、<code>回车</code>、<code>回车</code>、<code>回车</code>、<code>回车</code>、<code>w</code>直接使用默认值。</p>\n<p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/fdisk-n.png\" alt=\"分区\"></div></p>\n<h4 id=\"0x02：同步分区\">0x02：同步分区<a href=\"post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk#0x02：同步分区\"></a></h4>  <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">partprobe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>  <div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/partprobe.png\" alt=\"同步分区\"></div></p>\n<h4 id=\"0x03：设置文件系统\">0x03：设置文件系统<a href=\"post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk#0x03：设置文件系统\"></a></h4>  <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkfs -t ext4 /dev/vdb1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>  <div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/mkfs.png\" alt=\"设置文件系统\"></div></p>\n<h4 id=\"0x04：-挂载目录\">0x04： 挂载目录<a href=\"post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk#0x04：-挂载目录\"></a></h4>  <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir /disk</span><br><span class=\"line\">mount /dev/vdb1 /disk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>  <div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/mount.png\" alt=\"挂载目录\"></div></p>\n<h4 id=\"0x05：写入fstab\">0x05：写入fstab<a href=\"post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk#0x05：写入fstab\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">lsblk -f</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>获取到查看硬盘分区和 UUID后编辑<code>/etc/fstab</code>,并在最后一行写入：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">UUID=d668c5ac-d64c-4d27-a291-2ed695e61a0f /disk ext4 defaults 0 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>其中：<code>UUID</code>为<code>lsblk</code>查看的id,<code>/disk</code>为挂载目录，<code>ext4</code>为格式。</p>\n<h4 id=\"0x05：参考\">0x05：参考<a href=\"post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk#0x05：参考\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/document/product/1207/81981\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">腾讯轻量云挂载硬盘</a></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"利用Zerotier组网实现不同网络环境的主机互通互联","slug":"access-intranet-by-zerotier"},"next":{"title":"VS Code远程连接服务器及部署前端项目","slug":"remote_ssh_deploy"},"link":"https://www.alipay.one/post/mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk/"}